{"tid":410814,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩慘得過","createTime":"2017-09-23T09:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T11:32:37.000Z","uid":26728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"19a467e29a3f193db707fc332474f81e71d33a8b","tid":410814,"uid":26728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:25:14.000Z","msg":"佢有問題佢自己都知 但係就係唔肯為你改<br />\n你唔係唔愛佢 你甚至想同佢結婚行落去<br />\n但係佢個份自我中心嘅性格令到你越來越對佢卻步<br />\n<br />\n每一次嘈交就會做啲好傷你嘅嘢講啲好傷你嘅說話<br />\n你叫佢唔好咁講 點嘈都唔應該咁講咁做<br />\n佢就會話係你迫到佢咁 係你唔岩<br />\n一個男人 做完講完咁樣 真係岩咩？<br />\n<br />\n口邊不停掛住其實有無我都無所謂 其實自己一個更開心<br />\n每次嘈交都係我不停去哄 哄完又唔受 我都覺得頹<br />\n<br />\n雖然話條路係我自己簡 仆街唔好喊<br />\n<br />\n但係我都係忍唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f0d6ecde7adfaee8fc61353da45723e93f5053","tid":410814,"uid":26728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:32:52.000Z","msg":"1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b132ebe22636ead4c6043287f5ebb57447c5e46d","tid":410814,"uid":26728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:33:04.000Z","msg":"2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ea7ba291ebc98d75ee3a1c3b49003fdab9593d","tid":410814,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T10:00:18.000Z","msg":"fly lor"},{"pid":"720f75456940b86ec966f004a65a1fa716094046","tid":410814,"uid":71224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T10:03:11.000Z","msg":"既然你話佢唔肯改 拖得耐對大家都冇好處 快啲分手唔好浪費時間啦"},{"pid":"a59c81a783cdbafeab020da2a3f93d1e6982dcad","tid":410814,"uid":67069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy